evidence: It shows that the room temperature ductility of the RHEAs increases from 1.9% of the NbMoTaW RHEA to 11.5% of the TiNbMoTaW RHEA, and the yield strength increases from 996 MPa of the NbMoTaW RHEA to 1455 MPa of the TiNbMoTaW RHEA.

It shows that the room temperature ductility of the RHEAs increases from 1.9% of the NbMoTaW RHEA to 11.5% of the TiNbMoTaW RHEA, and the yield strength increases from 996 MPa of the NbMoTaW RHEA to 1455 MPa of the TiNbMoTaW RHEA.

The yield strength of the TiNbMoTaW alloy is 1455 MPa, which is 46% higher than that of NbMoTaW RHEA. While its ductility at room temperature is as high as 11.5%, which is about 5 times higher than that of NbMoTaW RHEA.
